            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "> During :restart it must also preserve the last state of NVIM server. correct me if I am wrong.\n\nI would say that is out of scope for this specific task. There is some discussion about that in https://github.com/neovim/neovim/issues/32471 , but it will involve improvements to `:mksession`, which is more involved than this specific story.\n\nThe specific goal of this issue is to restart the server and attach to it, without requiring the user to manually restart the UI and reattach to the new server.",
